(Translated by Google) there is a treasure hidden under a patch of peat buried in 1992. I can't say what it is, it's up to you to find out!

(Original)
il y a un trésors caché sous un carré de tourbe enterré en 1992. je ne peux pas dire c'est quoi, à vous de le découvrir !

(Translated by Google) Beautiful in summer as in winter
